.Dd $Mdocdate: October 24 2015 $
.Dt NL_LANGINFO 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm nl_langinfo
.Nd get locale information
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In langinfo.h
.Ft char *
.Fn nl_langinfo "nl_item item"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn nl_langinfo
function returns a pointer to a string containing information
set by the program's locale.
.Pp
The names and values of
.Fa item
are defined in
.In langinfo.h .
.Sh RETURN VALUES
.Fn nl_langinfo
returns a pointer to an empty string if
.Fa item
is invalid.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr setlocale 3
.Sh STANDARDS
The
.Fn nl_langinfo
function conforms to
.St -p1003.1-2008 .
